'''Jiotoermal ilekchrixiti''' a ilekchrixiti jinariet bai jiotoermal enaji. Teknalaji ina yuus ingkluud jrai stiim powa stieshan, flash stiim powa stieshan ah bainari saikl powa stieshan. Jiotoermal ilekchrixiti jinarieshan korantli yuuz ina 24 konchri,<ref name=gea2010>Geothermal Energy Association. [http://www.geo-energy.org/pdf/reports/GEA_International_Market_Report_Final_May_2010.pdf Geothermal Energy: International Market Update] May 2010, p. 4-6.</ref> wails [[jiotoermal iitin]] ina yuus ina 70 konchri.<ref name="IPCC">{{Citation |first1=Ingvar B. |last1=Fridleifsson, |first2=Ruggero |last2=Bertani |first3=Ernst |last3=Huenges |first4=John W. |last4=Lund |first5=Arni |last5=Ragnarsson |first6=Ladislaus |last6=Rybach |date=11 February 2008 |title=The possible role and contribution of geothermal energy to the mitigation of climate change |conference=IPCC Scoping Meeting on Renewable Energy Sources |editor=O. Hohmeyer and T. Trittin |location=Luebeck, Germany |pages=59–80 |url=http://iga.igg.cnr.it/documenti/IGA/Fridleifsson_et_al_IPCC_Geothermal_paper_2008.pdf |format=PDF |accessdate=6 April 2009}}</ref>

Az a 2015, wolwaid jiotoermal powa kiapasiti amount tu 12.8 [[gigawat]] (GW), outa we 28 posent ar 3,548 megawat instaal ina di [[Jiotoermal enaji ina di Yunaitid Stiet|Yunaitid Stiet]]. Intanashinal maakit eh-gruo a avrij anyual riet a 5 posent uoba di laas chrii ier ah gluobal jiotoermal powa kiapasiti expek fi kech 14.5–17.6&nbsp;GW bai 2020.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://geo-energy.org/reports/2015/Int'lMarketataGlanceMay2015Final5_14_15.pdf |title=The International Geothermal Market
At a Glance – May 2015 |publisher=GEA—Geothermal Energy Association |date=May 2015}}</ref> Bies pah korant jiolajik nalij ah teknalaji, di [[Jiotoermal Enaji Asosieshan]] (GEA) estimiet se onggl 6.5 posent a tuotal gluobal potenshal don-tap optel nou, wails di [[IPCC]] ripuot jiotoermal powa potenshal fi bi ina di rienj a 35&nbsp;GW tu 2&nbsp;[[terawat|TW]].<ref name="IPCC" /> Konchri we jinariet muo dah 15 posent a deh ilekchrixiti frah jiotoermal suos ingkluud [[Jiotoermal powa ina El Salvaduor|El Salvaduor]], [[Jiotoermal powa ina Kenia|Kenia]], di [[Jiotoermal powa ina di Filipiinz|Filipiinz]], [[Jiotoermal powa ina Aislan|Aislan]] ah [[Kasta Riika]].

